Sukma's dotfiles

Vim Setup

Requires NeoVim (>= 0.6)

- vim-plug - A minimalist Vim plugin manager: https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug

Shell Setup (macOS & Linux)

- Fish Shell: https://fishshell.com/
- Fisher - Plugin Manager: https://github.com/jorgebucaran/fisher
- Nerd Fonts - Powerline-patched fonts. I use Ioveska Term: https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts
- Exa - `ls` replacement: https://the.exa.website/
- z for fish - directory jumping: https://github.com/jethrokuan/z
